data.description: OPEN HOUSE Saturday, 12/2 from 1-4pm. Energy Efficient home with room for everyone at the Trails at Westpointe! You won't have to sweat the Summer energy bills because this home is equipped with Solar Panels that will be paid at closing. There is an Electric Vehicle charger outside the garage. The home has smart IKEA storage solutions throughout! The kitchen is decked out with granite counters, stainless steel appliances, a smart refrigerator and gas cooking. The washer and dryer will convey. This home has a secondary bedroom with an ensuite bathroom, perfect for a guest room or in-law suite. Upstairs you will find a game room and a dedicated media room. Plenty of space to spread out. Zoned to exemplary Northside ISD schools. Great access to Lackland AFB, Microsoft, Sea World and shopping. Schedule your showing today!
